A multivariable prediction model of a major treatment response for focal-onset 
seizures: A post-hoc analysis of Phase III trials of perampanel.

Krauss GL(1), Ben-Menachem E(2), Wechsler RT(3), Patten A(4), Williams B(5), 
Laurenza A(6), Malhotra M(7).

Author information:
(1)Johns Hopkins Hospital, 1800 Orleans Street, Baltimore, MD, 21287, USA. 
Electronic address: gkrauss@jhmi.edu.
(2)Sahlgrenska Academy, University of Gothenburg, Medicinaregatan 3, 413 90, 
Gothenburg, Sweden. Electronic address: elinor.ben-menachem@neuro.gu.se.
(3)Idaho Comprehensive Epilepsy Center, 1499 West Hays Street, Boise, ID, 83702, 
USA. Electronic address: rtw@idahoepilepsy.com.
(4)Eisai Ltd., Mosquito Way, Hatfield, Hertfordshire, AL10 9SN, UK. Electronic 
