Cost-utility analysis of a consensus and evidence-based medication review to 
optimize and potentially reduce psychotropic drug prescription in 
institutionalized dementia patients.

Massot Mesquida M(1)(2), Folkvord F(3)(4), Seda G(5)(6), Lupiáñez-Villanueva 
F(4)(7), Torán Monserrat P(5)(6).

Author information:
