Lanadelumab Efficacy, Safety, and Injection Interval Extension in HAE: A 
Real-Life Study.

Buttgereit T(1), Vera C(1), Weller K(1), Gutsche A(1), Grekowitz EM(1), Aykanat 
S(1), Wahn V(2), Krüger R(1), Maurer M(1), Magerl M(3).

Author information:
(1)Dermatological Allergology, Allergie-Centrum-Charité, Department of 
