Patient-relevant health outcomes for hemophilia care: Development of an 
international standard outcomes set.

van Balen EC(1), O'Mahony B(2), Cnossen MH(3), Dolan G(4), Blanchette VS(5), 
Fischer K(6), Gue D(7), O'Hara J(8), Iorio A(9)(10), Jackson S(7), Konkle 
